        "content": "<p>Shopify is a great shopping cart platform for an ecommerce website as it&#39;s easy to set up a site and have control over it. An advantage of out of the box commerce platforms, like Shopify, as well as several alternatives to Shopify, is control over design of your site without having to use your own server. For small business owners, you will notice Shopify offers you a wide variety of tools to alter your store. The AppStore available for its users contains many interesting plugins to customize your website.<br />\n<br />\nHowever, despite all it&#39;s features, Shopify is expensive especially for a small business owner. Additionally, the lack of content marketing features make it hard to promote your product. Content marketing opportunities are key for choosing a digital commerce provider, as marketing powers revenue growth. There are also other issues that may cause you to consider switching to a Shopify competitor, as today&#39;s Shopify alternatives might satisfy your needs.&nbsp;</p>\n",
